snippet.title: Longplay of Capcom Puzzle World
snippet.description:
Longplay of Capcom Puzzle World, played  as the NTSC version on the PlayStation Portable. This game's version was released on February 6, 2007. Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!

0:00:00 - Start
0:00:23 - Super Puzzle Fighter II Turbo
0:04:25 - Buster Bros.
0:07:31 - Super Buster Bros.
0:09:42 - Buster Buddies
0:12:22 - Block Block
0:14:30 - Credits

By: Val
